skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: tommy bear movies
des:
Say a movie title and it will tell you when it was made, who starred in it, who directed it, what it grossed, and what it is rated. 

Or say "start a quiz" and it will ask you a 10 question quiz about when 10 movies were made. When it gives you the answer it will tell you other relevant information about the movie. The database contains almost 4000 movies.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
